STACK:
  - React 19 + Vite
  - Firebase v11 (Auth, Firestore, Functions, Hosting)
  - Tailwind CSS 4
  - TypeScript strict mode

CONVENTIONS:
  - One React component per file
  - kebab-case Firestore collections
  - PascalCase React components
  - Cloud Functions handle all writes and validation

SECURITY:
  - Firebase Auth (Google SSO)
  - UID-based access control
  - All writes via Cloud Functions only

TESTS:
  - Jest + React Testing Library for frontend
  - @firebase/rules-unit-testing for backend
  - Emulator Suite required for local dev
